    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We always understood why and how one experiences emotions, but we could never <strong><i>see</i></strong> why.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This changed, however, once a governmental medical institution made a discovery. A way to manifest human thoughts and emotions into a <i><strong>visible entity</strong></i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To monitor these entities, a Japanese prefecture has been turned into a labyrinth-like net of hospitals. All of this is for the sake of acquiring complete emotional stability through the removal of illegal emotional states.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this environment, a young distressed student named Lia experiences her inner problems through many changes in her own <strong><i>manifestation of emotions</i></strong>. Can you help Lia cope with her emotions and her inner voice through your choices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...or will you give in to your negative thoughts?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Hand-drawn game</strong> - a comic style visual novel </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Branching narrative</strong> - your choices do make a difference; explore different emotional states Lia can find herself in through other available choices </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings</strong> - replay the game, and you may get a different ending; choices change the state of your &quot;emotion scanner&quot; you'll see pop up in the corner of your screen from time to time, maybe you can let it guide you</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minigame</strong> - a simple multiple-choice game of point &amp; click, with elements  that will help you get desired emotions; help Lia navigate through her feelings and focus on the wanted outcome </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original story and Art</strong> - a stylized approach to a dystopian world </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original soundtrack</strong> - musical ambiance for the exploration of an emotion-monitored world </p></li></ul>",
